d\" data-text=\"Luci\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"patronym\" data-text=\"Luci\">L</span></span>·F·AEM(<em>scil.</em> TRIBU)<span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Fir\"><span data-text=\"Fir\">FIR</span></span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]</span><br id=\"al2-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span>P·PEC[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]INPEN[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]</span></div><p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div>"
